WEBVTT

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:16.200
You have to look for him in the Life Spirit Realm.

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:17.640
Thank you.

00:00:17.920 --> 00:00:19.200
But I think I like it here.

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:21.000
Don’t do this.

00:00:21.440 --> 00:00:23.640
You’re very important to me.

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:28.640
If I go with you,

00:00:28.920 --> 00:00:30.080
I’ll become Wu, won’t I?

00:00:30.640 --> 00:00:31.040
Yes.

00:00:31.720 --> 00:00:33.440
You’ll be the coolest Wu ever.

00:00:36.080 --> 00:00:37.040
Niran is awake now.

00:00:44.400 --> 00:00:47.040
WHEN THE WORLD KNEW WHAT BEAUTY WAS, UGLINESS WAS BORN.

00:00:47.040 --> 00:00:49.360
WHEN THE WORLD KNEW WHAT GOOD WAS, EVIL WAS BORN.

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:59.160
CHIANG RAI, 2005

00:00:59.880 --> 00:01:04.000
(Ever since the government declared war on narcotics,)

00:01:04.319 --> 00:01:07.960
(the number of drug users has significantly dwindled.)

00:01:08.120 --> 00:01:12.120
(However, there is also a high number of casualties from the same measure.)

00:01:13.160 --> 00:01:13.680
Damn.

00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:17.640
This is so sick, man.

00:01:18.280 --> 00:01:19.000
Li Puo.

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:22.120
We’re celebrating today because you got into university, you know?

00:01:22.240 --> 00:01:24.039
Why aren’t you drinking with us?

00:01:24.440 --> 00:01:26.120
Who’d drive you idiots if I drank?

00:01:27.080 --> 00:01:28.000
How nice of you!

00:01:28.120 --> 00:01:28.600
Hey, jerk!

00:01:29.120 --> 00:01:31.320
You gonna forget us once you’re a college student?

00:01:32.440 --> 00:01:33.560
This is so sick, dude.

00:01:33.560 --> 00:01:34.520
It is, dude!

00:01:36.440 --> 00:01:37.280
Drink up!

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:37.840
My pleasure!

00:01:38.280 --> 00:01:39.400
Hey, don’t spill anything.

00:01:42.080 --> 00:01:43.080
Let’s go somewhere after.

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:44.200
So damn fun.

00:01:46.560 --> 00:01:46.960
Oi.

00:01:47.800 --> 00:01:48.560
Why did you pull over?

00:01:49.320 --> 00:01:50.039
I need to take a piss.

00:01:50.840 --> 00:01:51.800
Just wait for me here.

00:01:52.479 --> 00:01:54.840
It’s a damn bad time to take a piss, Li Puo!

00:02:02.040 --> 00:02:04.240
What’d you need to go so deep into the woods for?

00:02:04.400 --> 00:02:06.960
You afraid we’d find out your dick’s small?

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:12.240
Those loud-mouth idiots…

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:18.320
Oh?

00:02:32.680 --> 00:02:34.079
What are you doing here?

00:02:35.040 --> 00:02:36.200
We’re on our way home, sir.

00:02:36.800 --> 00:02:37.960
Why don’t you get out here and talk?

00:02:38.640 --> 00:02:39.440
Is something the matter?

00:02:40.440 --> 00:02:41.320
Just do what I say.

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:42.040
Get out.

00:02:53.960 --> 00:02:55.360
Hey!

00:03:06.880 --> 00:03:07.320
Hey!

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:36.720
Hey, why the hell did you stop?

00:03:37.520 --> 00:03:38.120
Keep digging!

00:03:42.480 --> 00:03:43.400
Shit!

00:04:48.760 --> 00:04:50.680
Dear Lord Warrior,

00:04:52.080 --> 00:04:57.320
please give me the strength to handle the obstacles in our way.

00:06:43.560 --> 00:06:44.440
What do we do now?

00:06:52.400 --> 00:06:53.960
Should we just look up the next best timing to seal it again?

00:06:54.600 --> 00:06:57.320
But there are so many life spirits devoured by Qi Rong.

00:06:57.840 --> 00:07:00.920
Shouldn’t we… try and save those people?

00:07:01.840 --> 00:07:03.160
Is there a way to do that?

00:07:04.840 --> 00:07:06.240
Of course, there is.

00:07:09.160 --> 00:07:11.160
And you came up with it, Niran.

00:07:14.560 --> 00:07:16.120
We just have to repeat what we did.

00:07:16.880 --> 00:07:18.360
We seal Qi Rong,

00:07:19.160 --> 00:07:21.160
and then destroy the seal.

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:25.280
A sealed Qi Rong will come out weakened,

00:07:25.440 --> 00:07:28.040
and the life spirits that have been devoured will squeeze their way out

00:07:28.200 --> 00:07:29.560
and find their way to their body.

00:07:30.200 --> 00:07:32.720
That’s when we seal it again.

00:07:33.680 --> 00:07:34.360
Right after.

00:07:36.440 --> 00:07:37.080
Crap.

00:07:37.680 --> 00:07:39.120
But we could barely survive one ritual.

00:07:42.159 --> 00:07:43.440
Our priority right now,

00:07:44.159 --> 00:07:45.680
I think, is to keep a low profile.

00:07:47.200 --> 00:07:48.480
Especially you, Niran.

00:07:48.920 --> 00:07:50.840
We can’t let Li Puo know you’re alive.

00:07:51.520 --> 00:07:52.960
He will only find another way to attack you.

00:07:56.200 --> 00:07:57.760
I found his date and time of birth.

00:07:58.120 --> 00:08:00.080
LI PUO SAEMING, BORNNOVEMBER 18, 1987, 5.59 P.M.
This is what I got.

00:08:00.720 --> 00:08:04.360
This means right now he can’t attack you with his dark arts.

00:08:04.640 --> 00:08:07.240
But it doesn’t mean he can’t do you harm, Niran.

00:08:08.480 --> 00:08:09.520
We’re better safe than sorry.

00:08:27.560 --> 00:08:29.600
You need to think about our party in a time like this.

00:08:30.040 --> 00:08:32.280
Otherwise, in the next election,

00:08:32.960 --> 00:08:35.039
we’ll lose a lot of our MPs to the other parties.

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:36.280
Do you,

00:08:37.799 --> 00:08:38.799
or all of you,

00:08:40.200 --> 00:08:43.960
think I should prioritize our party over our country?

00:08:47.720 --> 00:08:49.280
I heard that

00:08:49.720 --> 00:08:52.720
that if we fail to stabilize our legislation,

00:08:53.600 --> 00:08:56.880
our coalition parties will back off and join the opposition instead.

00:08:58.240 --> 00:09:00.240
Then we should simply dissolve the parliament.

00:09:00.600 --> 00:09:01.880
If we do that right now,

00:09:01.960 --> 00:09:04.640
we’re definitely going to be the opposition in the next election.

00:09:04.880 --> 00:09:05.960
Do you have a better idea?

00:09:15.320 --> 00:09:18.400
So none of you have a solution for me?

00:09:35.520 --> 00:09:36.000
Come.

00:09:37.040 --> 00:09:37.480
Cheers!

00:09:39.440 --> 00:09:41.960
Thank you for all your hard work.

00:09:42.520 --> 00:09:43.120
Cheers.

00:09:49.960 --> 00:09:52.480
The Prime Minister finally decided to take a step back.

00:09:53.800 --> 00:09:54.880
So your job here is done.

00:09:55.520 --> 00:09:58.200
You can call off the protests tomorrow.

00:10:01.280 --> 00:10:04.400
Sir, the people have taken to the sentiment.

00:10:05.080 --> 00:10:07.040
You can’t just tell them to stop.

00:10:07.520 --> 00:10:12.160
They are calling for a change in leadership.

00:10:12.280 --> 00:10:13.360
Without that,

00:10:13.360 --> 00:10:15.200
they will never back down.

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:16.480
What the hell!

00:10:16.720 --> 00:10:18.800
Aren’t they all hired hands?

00:10:19.120 --> 00:10:20.800
Why can’t I tell them to stop?

00:10:21.200 --> 00:10:21.760
You’re right.

00:10:22.120 --> 00:10:25.360
The initial protesters were hired.

00:10:25.480 --> 00:10:30.640
But right now, more than 80% is just people who show up on their own.

00:10:30.840 --> 00:10:34.160
This is no longer your business, sir.

00:10:34.320 --> 00:10:36.520
I think you might need to have the Prime Minister make a public statement first

00:10:36.720 --> 00:10:37.880
before things can get better.

00:10:38.040 --> 00:10:38.840
I don’t give a shit!

00:10:39.560 --> 00:10:41.160
You must follow my orders!

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:44.760
Whatever it is, I am not paying youa single dime more.

00:10:44.880 --> 00:10:45.600
Damn it!

00:11:02.400 --> 00:11:03.760
What is this?

00:11:08.320 --> 00:11:09.640
What the hell is this?

00:11:11.360 --> 00:11:12.280
You!

00:11:48.160 --> 00:11:49.840
You are right.

00:11:51.560 --> 00:11:53.880
This is no longer Master’s business.

00:11:57.640 --> 00:12:00.200
Nor is it yours.

00:12:21.760 --> 00:12:23.240
The greatest power

00:12:24.560 --> 00:12:27.200
will never belong to a mere human being.

00:12:53.480 --> 00:12:54.160
Why are you calling me now?

00:12:55.200 --> 00:12:55.680
What do you want?

00:12:56.080 --> 00:12:57.480
(Rest assured, Mr. Prime Minister.)

00:12:59.280 --> 00:13:03.040
From now on, Baocheng is no longer your concern.

00:13:06.280 --> 00:13:07.040
(What do you mean?)

00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:12.880
Baocheng thought he could control winds and storms.

00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:16.440
But he has been bashed by them.

00:13:17.920 --> 00:13:19.680
Now it’s just you, sir.

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:24.840
This might be a good time for you to prove yourself to the Lord.

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:29.680
The Prime Minister of this nation
does not need to prove himself to no one,

00:13:29.920 --> 00:13:30.880
but his people.

00:13:37.600 --> 00:13:38.560
(Mr. Prime Minister,)

00:13:39.480 --> 00:13:43.440
the power of Lord Warrior has taken over this entire city.

00:13:44.360 --> 00:13:51.080
Only the strongest has the power to rule over this city of angels.

00:14:10.920 --> 00:14:14.880
STATE OF EMERGENCY DICTATES NO MORE THAN FIVE GATHERING
The government has just declared a state of emergency,

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:17.080
preventing gatherings of more than five people.

00:14:17.200 --> 00:14:20.880
There is also a curfew from midnight to 4 a.m.

00:14:21.760 --> 00:14:26.040
However, no comments have been given on the disappearance of

00:14:26.120 --> 00:14:27.440
the leaders of the protests.

00:14:27.520 --> 00:14:32.440
(But social commentary mostly agrees that they were made to disappear.)

00:14:32.520 --> 00:14:34.120
Don’t watch it if it’s depressing.

00:14:34.720 --> 00:14:35.680
What’s with you?

00:14:40.040 --> 00:14:41.600
Your house is on fire,

00:14:42.000 --> 00:14:44.200
and you don’t give a damn about it?

00:14:45.320 --> 00:14:46.520
A fire, huh…

00:14:46.800 --> 00:14:50.040
If your house is on fire,your brain will automatically tell you what to do.

00:14:50.480 --> 00:14:52.840
But since you have time to stress over it,

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:55.400
the house hasn’t caught on fire yet.

00:15:03.880 --> 00:15:04.560
What was that?

00:15:04.800 --> 00:15:06.680
Wanna know, don’t you?

00:15:07.160 --> 00:15:08.480
I read somewhere online

00:15:08.800 --> 00:15:10.560
that a machine that’s been working too hard

00:15:11.120 --> 00:15:12.800
needs to be unplugged from time to time.

00:15:13.520 --> 00:15:14.720
Same goes for you.

00:15:21.040 --> 00:15:21.800
Turn off!

00:15:28.720 --> 00:15:29.360
What the hell?

00:15:29.880 --> 00:15:30.400
You idiot.

00:15:30.800 --> 00:15:32.040
You’re a damn dork.

00:15:34.280 --> 00:15:37.280
You were helping me with my work.

00:15:37.960 --> 00:15:39.040
So you must be tired, too.

00:15:42.440 --> 00:15:42.640
I—

00:15:42.680 --> 00:15:43.160
Turn off!

00:15:43.360 --> 00:15:44.960
Idiot! I’m a limited edition machine!

00:15:45.200 --> 00:15:45.840
Watch it.

00:15:47.760 --> 00:15:49.120
What a dork.

00:15:52.760 --> 00:15:55.800
Your problem is that you’re cooped up here.

00:16:03.560 --> 00:16:04.560
Why don’t you come take a ride with me?

00:16:06.600 --> 00:16:07.280
What are you talking about?

00:16:08.760 --> 00:16:10.240
I need to hide from Li Puo.

00:16:10.960 --> 00:16:11.960
I can’t go anywhere with you.

00:16:12.560 --> 00:16:14.040
Oh, come on.

00:16:14.640 --> 00:16:16.200
It’s 10 p.m.

00:16:16.720 --> 00:16:18.680
I’m sure even Li Puo needs to sleep, too.

00:16:19.200 --> 00:16:21.720
He’s not gonna possess some animal to keep an eye on you all day, you know?

00:16:27.520 --> 00:16:27.760
Come on.

00:16:40.680 --> 00:16:42.000
Loosen up!

00:16:42.560 --> 00:16:42.920
What?

00:16:43.200 --> 00:16:43.560
What did you say?

00:16:44.040 --> 00:16:45.560
I said loosen up!

00:16:45.880 --> 00:16:47.360
Well, you’re going too fast!

00:16:47.720 --> 00:16:48.800
Trust me a little, will you?

00:16:52.280 --> 00:16:52.920
Hold on tight.

00:16:55.920 --> 00:16:56.960
You’re really going too fast, Pete.

00:16:57.720 --> 00:16:58.680
Just trust me.

00:17:45.880 --> 00:17:47.160
I’ll teach you something.

00:17:47.320 --> 00:17:47.720
What?

00:17:48.360 --> 00:17:49.200
Just follow my lead.

00:17:50.760 --> 00:17:51.080
You idiot!

00:17:51.360 --> 00:17:51.600
Careful!

00:17:53.080 --> 00:17:53.520
Go on.

00:17:57.600 --> 00:17:57.960
Come on.

00:17:59.080 --> 00:18:00.400
One, two, three.

00:18:10.520 --> 00:18:11.960
Hey! Don’t let go of your hands!

00:18:19.560 --> 00:18:20.880
(Gung once taught me that)

00:18:21.360 --> 00:18:23.680
(when one’s spirit is weak,)

00:18:24.240 --> 00:18:26.000
(one must look for a connection.)

00:18:27.040 --> 00:18:30.480
(For that is the source of energy that will keep one whole.)

00:18:33.880 --> 00:18:35.080
(I remember that.)

00:18:37.080 --> 00:18:39.120
(I just never understood it…)

00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:42.720
(until now.)

00:19:05.000 --> 00:19:07.040
Actually, ever since you passed away, Gung,

00:19:07.840 --> 00:19:09.280
I’ve met you several times.

00:19:11.200 --> 00:19:12.480
Sometimes in my dreams.

00:19:13.720 --> 00:19:14.720
Sometimes in my thoughts.

00:19:15.680 --> 00:19:16.720
But this…

00:19:19.840 --> 00:19:21.120
This is the first time

00:19:22.080 --> 00:19:23.480
it feels like

00:19:24.160 --> 00:19:25.880
I really am meeting you.

00:19:34.360 --> 00:19:35.000
Gung.

00:19:37.920 --> 00:19:39.320
Is that really you?

00:19:40.760 --> 00:19:41.880
Or am I just in my head?

00:19:48.200 --> 00:19:51.560
No one can answer you that

00:19:51.960 --> 00:19:53.200
but yourself.

00:19:54.760 --> 00:19:55.760
If it really is you, Gung,

00:19:58.480 --> 00:19:59.960
where have you been all this time?

00:20:02.560 --> 00:20:04.000
Why did you come to me now?

00:20:05.760 --> 00:20:08.120
I am a part of nature.

00:20:09.360 --> 00:20:11.440
If you can feel nature,

00:20:12.520 --> 00:20:17.960
then you must know that I’m with you all the time.

00:20:19.040 --> 00:20:20.600
I am never far away.

00:20:29.120 --> 00:20:31.200
Any more questions?

00:20:39.320 --> 00:20:40.440
No.

00:20:43.520 --> 00:20:45.240
I have nothing more to ask.

00:20:47.640 --> 00:20:50.640
That’s why we’re meeting right now.

00:21:23.280 --> 00:21:23.720
Niran.

00:21:27.520 --> 00:21:29.160
Are you sure you’re ready to leave the hospital?

00:21:32.880 --> 00:21:34.920
I just think it’s about time I stop hiding.

00:21:41.440 --> 00:21:43.720
I’ll let heaven lead the way.

00:21:44.640 --> 00:21:46.960
Whatever happens happens.

00:21:50.760 --> 00:21:52.560
Ever since coming back from the death,

00:21:52.800 --> 00:21:53.800
you’ve been so mature, you idiot.

00:21:55.040 --> 00:21:57.520
As if a guy like me would be at death’s door so easily.

00:22:12.480 --> 00:22:14.640
Do you remember what happened when you were there?

00:22:19.080 --> 00:22:20.720
You’re important to people,

00:22:21.360 --> 00:22:23.000
at least to me.

00:22:27.200 --> 00:22:29.840
I… don’t remember what happened exactly.

00:22:37.240 --> 00:22:38.400
But I remember how it felt.

00:22:50.800 --> 00:22:53.040
I really thought I’d lose you, you know.

00:22:58.040 --> 00:23:03.480
Thank you for doing everything in your power to bring me back.

00:23:05.240 --> 00:23:07.320
Why did you believe in me?

00:23:08.760 --> 00:23:09.840
And I’m not just talking about this,

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:14.960
but everything that’s happened from the first day you met me.

00:23:18.880 --> 00:23:20.480
I was a dickhead.

00:23:23.360 --> 00:23:25.560
Why didn’t you give up on me?

00:23:28.600 --> 00:23:29.600
It was all you.

00:23:31.120 --> 00:23:32.320
You didn’t give up on yourself.

00:23:39.000 --> 00:23:40.120
Honestly…

00:23:41.480 --> 00:23:42.920
I don’t think I could have done any of that

00:23:45.760 --> 00:23:47.680
if no one believes in me.

00:23:52.240 --> 00:23:53.440
But you do.

00:23:58.040 --> 00:24:01.280
Maybe the reason I agreed to come back

00:24:02.440 --> 00:24:03.960
was exactly that.

00:24:08.840 --> 00:24:12.000
At least I have you who truly believes in me.

00:24:22.920 --> 00:24:24.240
What’s not to believe in?

00:25:00.200 --> 00:25:01.000
Niran?

00:25:01.920 --> 00:25:03.040
How did you come back?

00:25:48.160 --> 00:25:49.680
I really can’t believe

00:25:50.240 --> 00:25:52.320
that a guy like you would survive that.

00:25:53.640 --> 00:25:55.400
Why are you doing this, Li Puo?

00:25:56.320 --> 00:25:58.240
I thought you were just serving your master,

00:25:59.480 --> 00:26:01.080
but it seems that isn’t the case.

00:26:01.600 --> 00:26:03.280
I am serving my master.

00:26:03.840 --> 00:26:06.160
My Master just happens to be Lord Warrior.

00:26:06.920 --> 00:26:07.960
What are you thinking?

00:26:09.200 --> 00:26:10.120
What exactly do you want?

00:26:10.120 --> 00:26:11.320
I don’t want anything.

00:26:13.120 --> 00:26:16.720
I just want to be the one who brings my God his freedom,

00:26:17.880 --> 00:26:20.280
so he can use his power with liberty.

00:26:21.360 --> 00:26:22.760
Listen to me, Li Puo.

00:26:23.560 --> 00:26:26.000
There is no liberty when it comes to a demon’s power.

00:26:26.600 --> 00:26:27.920
That’s the rules of heaven.

00:26:29.160 --> 00:26:30.600
Rules of heaven, huh?

00:26:31.520 --> 00:26:32.960
Who does heaven think it is?

00:26:33.560 --> 00:26:34.880
What right does it have to make up these rules?

00:26:36.440 --> 00:26:39.960
You still truly believe in that childish story, Niran?

00:26:43.480 --> 00:26:45.600
If ‘heaven’ truly is righteous,

00:26:47.520 --> 00:26:49.160
how come it ignores pain?

00:26:49.800 --> 00:26:51.560
How come it neglects ill fates?

00:26:52.200 --> 00:26:54.720
How come it never listens, never helps?

00:26:57.520 --> 00:27:00.520
Am I but a lowlife human being,

00:27:02.200 --> 00:27:06.160
too low that I disgust the almighty and delightful heaven?

00:27:10.040 --> 00:27:11.360
Heaven is without justice,

00:27:12.040 --> 00:27:13.360
and still dares to make rules?

00:27:16.240 --> 00:27:16.680
Yes.

00:27:18.520 --> 00:27:19.600
You might be right.

00:27:22.400 --> 00:27:23.400
Heaven does not empathize,

00:27:24.520 --> 00:27:25.600
Heaven doesn’t play favorites,

00:27:26.640 --> 00:27:27.320
nor favor.

00:27:28.520 --> 00:27:29.320
is no one’s friend,

00:27:30.560 --> 00:27:31.920
nor helps a single soul.

00:27:33.240 --> 00:27:36.640
But that’s what makes heaven impartial,

00:27:37.520 --> 00:27:39.560
and suitable to make rules.

00:27:41.120 --> 00:27:43.240
The power of evil you’re chasing after,

00:27:44.760 --> 00:27:48.400
do you really think it gives a damn about you?

00:27:54.440 --> 00:27:56.720
When heaven abandoned me,

00:27:57.360 --> 00:27:58.960
left me less than a human being,

00:27:59.920 --> 00:28:07.600
only my God saw me, gave me strength, and kept me alive to this day.

00:28:09.320 --> 00:28:11.760
Where was heaven?

00:28:12.400 --> 00:28:14.160
What was it doing when I needed it most?

00:28:18.480 --> 00:28:21.360
You think the demon gives you strength.

00:28:23.080 --> 00:28:23.480
But no…

00:28:25.400 --> 00:28:26.880
The more you can’t live without it,

00:28:28.560 --> 00:28:30.240
the weaker you become.

00:28:39.360 --> 00:28:40.480
Weak, am I?

00:28:41.680 --> 00:28:44.680
That’s rich coming from the guy who almost died by my hand.

00:28:45.400 --> 00:28:47.960
I guess you need a tougher lesson.

00:28:48.800 --> 00:28:50.080
All you have of me is a scrap of my blood.

00:28:51.360 --> 00:28:53.000
But I know your time of birth.

00:28:56.880 --> 00:28:58.760
I’m afraid your black magic won’t work on me anymore.

00:29:00.960 --> 00:29:01.720
Well, then…

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:05.440
Lord Warrior will deal with you himself.

00:29:06.560 --> 00:29:06.920
Oh?

00:29:08.360 --> 00:29:09.560
From where I’m standing,

00:29:10.200 --> 00:29:13.680
it was me who almost dealt with your god.

00:29:13.840 --> 00:29:14.480
Niran!

00:29:14.480 --> 00:29:16.120
And even if I can’t seal him this time,

00:29:17.160 --> 00:29:19.240
heaven will deal with him.

00:29:20.200 --> 00:29:22.280
Any power that defies nature

00:29:22.800 --> 00:29:24.680
will never last long.

00:29:43.000 --> 00:29:44.080
Niran.

00:29:49.560 --> 00:29:50.760
Niran.

00:30:35.000 --> 00:30:35.960
(Why did you pull over?)

00:30:36.320 --> 00:30:37.800
(What the hell?)

00:30:37.840 --> 00:30:39.280
(Do you want to be the next corpse?)

00:30:44.480 --> 00:30:47.640
Stop being pathetic, you coward!

00:30:59.400 --> 00:31:00.560
My pupil.

00:31:02.000 --> 00:31:02.920
Lord Warrior.

00:31:18.120 --> 00:31:19.200
Lord Warrior?

00:31:38.120 --> 00:31:39.280
My pupil.

00:31:40.320 --> 00:31:42.920
I saved you, showed you the way.

00:31:43.720 --> 00:31:46.360
Now it is time

00:31:47.080 --> 00:31:49.520
for you to protect me.

00:32:56.440 --> 00:32:57.440
What happened?

00:32:59.200 --> 00:33:00.520
Why didn’t the demon show up?

00:33:39.760 --> 00:33:41.600
Lord Warrior,

00:33:41.600 --> 00:33:44.080
when you reside in this body,

00:33:44.080 --> 00:33:47.680
Niran will never be able to seal you ever again.

00:33:47.760 --> 00:33:52.560
Please take residence in this body I acquired for you.

00:34:39.120 --> 00:34:39.840
Lord Warrior?

00:34:56.400 --> 00:34:57.320
Lord Warrior.

00:34:58.840 --> 00:35:00.720
Lord Warrior, please do not be enraged.

00:35:00.720 --> 00:35:02.160
This is only temporary.

00:35:02.160 --> 00:35:04.360
Until I deal with Niran…

00:35:39.680 --> 00:35:40.600
Li Puo…

00:35:41.880 --> 00:35:42.880
He must have done something.

00:36:02.120 --> 00:36:02.720
Li Puo!

00:36:04.160 --> 00:36:04.920
What happened?

00:36:30.040 --> 00:36:33.040
Guide… me.

00:36:49.160 --> 00:36:51.360
If you allow your mind to be a sponge,

00:36:53.000 --> 00:36:54.480
when evil is near,

00:36:55.800 --> 00:36:57.080
you will absorb it.

00:36:59.680 --> 00:37:01.320
But if allow your mind to be a mirror,

00:37:03.840 --> 00:37:05.880
everything will be nothing but a reflection.

00:37:08.080 --> 00:37:11.040
No absorbing, no misleading.

00:37:18.320 --> 00:37:23.280
And no evil in the world can touch you.

00:37:56.480 --> 00:37:58.440
Why would Li Puo do this?

00:37:59.040 --> 00:38:02.760
He must have thought it was the only way Qi Rong could evade the sealing.

00:38:03.240 --> 00:38:06.880
Inhabiting a human body does have certain freedom.

00:38:07.800 --> 00:38:09.080
Then he was a damn fool.

00:38:09.480 --> 00:38:13.560
Imagine being a great powerful force
that’s survived for thousands of years

00:38:13.800 --> 00:38:18.280
and some random dude puts you in a weak and dirty vessel like that…

00:38:18.480 --> 00:38:20.280
I would have slaughtered him, too.

00:38:24.640 --> 00:38:25.760
Li Puo was misguided.

00:38:27.000 --> 00:38:29.080
He thought Qi Rong would cherish and have mercy on him.

00:38:30.440 --> 00:38:34.960
But in reality, any higher power

00:38:36.600 --> 00:38:39.480
is incapable of playing favorites with any human being.

00:38:41.880 --> 00:38:43.080
Be that heaven or demons,

00:38:44.840 --> 00:38:45.920
they’re no different.

00:39:02.320 --> 00:39:02.920
Yes.

00:39:04.440 --> 00:39:05.440
They’re no different.

00:39:09.360 --> 00:39:13.760
Does that mean the first seal was already done by Li Puo?

00:39:15.160 --> 00:39:15.520
Yes.

00:39:17.000 --> 00:39:20.560
I believe everyone whose life spirits were devoured is awake now.

00:39:21.320 --> 00:39:23.200
All we need to do is begin the second seal.

00:40:36.360 --> 00:40:37.080
Well?

00:40:37.840 --> 00:40:40.240
Does the fresh air make you feel better?

00:40:43.040 --> 00:40:43.760
Yeah.

00:40:45.400 --> 00:40:47.560
But we have a curfew, right?

00:40:48.000 --> 00:40:49.320
Don’t we need to get going?

00:40:49.600 --> 00:40:50.960
Oh, forget it.

00:40:51.120 --> 00:40:52.640
Arrest me if they have to.

00:40:53.040 --> 00:40:53.360
Oh?

00:40:53.800 --> 00:40:56.640
It’s too much trouble, don’t you think?

00:40:56.880 --> 00:40:58.800
It’s so impossible to live nowadays.

00:40:58.920 --> 00:41:01.240
I swear the world felt much more peaceful when I was a kid.

00:41:01.280 --> 00:41:02.360
But now that I’m an adult?

00:41:02.400 --> 00:41:03.680
Damn it.

00:41:04.120 --> 00:41:05.600
What a messy world we live in!

00:41:05.600 --> 00:41:06.760
Look around you.

00:41:14.880 --> 00:41:18.480
The original state of the universe was never peaceful, you know?

00:41:20.360 --> 00:41:21.960
Before heaven separated from earth,

00:41:23.720 --> 00:41:27.000
what reigned over the world was chaos.

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:32.840
So I guess it’s not strange chaos persists through every age.

00:41:35.120 --> 00:41:35.920
But I think

00:41:37.160 --> 00:41:38.640
that peace you felt when you were a kid

00:41:39.800 --> 00:41:41.800
came from your own mind.

00:41:44.960 --> 00:41:45.680
You’re right.

00:41:46.120 --> 00:41:48.000
I didn’t know anything as a kid.

00:41:48.480 --> 00:41:50.160
I was just living my life.

00:41:51.680 --> 00:41:53.280
I didn’t give a damn about nothing.

00:41:53.640 --> 00:41:55.160
No wonder I grew up to be an idiot.

00:41:56.040 --> 00:41:56.640
Not at all.

00:41:57.800 --> 00:42:00.800
You grew up in a close-knitted family.

00:42:01.640 --> 00:42:06.000
The love your family had for you made you feel safe.

00:42:06.880 --> 00:42:10.120
That was why the whole world felt safe to you.

00:42:11.840 --> 00:42:13.720
Just like when I was with Gung.

00:42:17.680 --> 00:42:18.680
Thank you.

00:42:21.480 --> 00:42:23.280
You risked your life to save me

00:42:24.440 --> 00:42:27.240
when you honestly didn’t have to.

00:42:29.480 --> 00:42:29.920
No.

00:42:30.880 --> 00:42:31.640
I totally had to.

00:42:32.560 --> 00:42:34.640
When someone I love is in danger,

00:42:35.960 --> 00:42:39.520
be that my friend, my sibling, or my buddy,

00:42:40.560 --> 00:42:41.760
I do need to save them.

00:43:05.640 --> 00:43:07.400
Be that heaven or demons, they’re no different.

00:43:07.400 --> 00:43:10.440
I bow my humble head to the great and powerful Lord Warrior.

00:43:10.920 --> 00:43:13.160
I have an important statement to make.

00:43:13.440 --> 00:43:14.640
The government just came out and said

00:43:14.640 --> 00:43:16.600
they’ll use real weapons in dealing with protesters.

00:43:16.680 --> 00:43:17.200
Fei.

00:43:17.560 --> 00:43:19.400
You need to take me to the Prime Minister right now.

00:43:19.760 --> 00:43:24.880
Will you allow me to perform a ritual to see if the mandate of heaven is still with you?

00:43:25.840 --> 00:43:26.480
What the hell?